title: I can't see club tags in-game
body:
So, basically i can't see the clubs while i am in-game. I asked 1 friend if he sees them and he said "yes".
How i can make them on in-game, please help!

replies.body: What's the name of the club you're trying to find? It might be due to some special characters perhaps, but there's also a small bug with clubs that can only be fixed once I know the name of the messed up club. Hit me back up and I'll poke around to see if I can fix it!

The club's name is ÝΔ$UØ in EUNE.
While I am in-game I can't see other clubs too only when I press tab and i put my mouse on their names only then I can see them.
